fields.name: Effect:
fields.value: Attack another player for 2 HP. You will get the card back at the end of the phase if undefended.

fields.name: Upgraded:
fields.value:
Attack another player for 2 HP. You will get this card back at the end of the phase the first two times you use this card, regardless of what happens. 

*This card will come back to you __at the end of the phase__ as long as the target is shown to not defend!*
